name: Flare-S Racing Swoop
Lore: 'Attain speeds of up to 600 kph. 3 meters long. Extremely difficult to control at high speeds. Dengar rode a similar swoop when injured in a race with Han at Agrilat.',
Text: 'May add 1 driver and 1 passenger. Landspeed = driver''s ability, and may be used at any time to follow an opponent''s vehicle or character that just moved from same site (if within range).',
